post_install() {
  cat << EOF

betterdiscord-rauenzi-git requires you to install per-user. To install:
  $ betterdiscordctl install -c -b /usr/lib/betterdiscord-rauenzi-git
To remove:
  $ betterdiscordctl uninstall

If BetterDiscord stops working, try uninstalling and reinstalling. If it
continues to fail, leave an issue at:
  https://github.com/bb010g/betterdiscordctl/issues

EOF
}
